article_title: Few health care options for low-income Kansans
article_text:
Most uninsured Kansans are working

Make too much to qualify for Medicaid

Make too little to qualify for insurance subsidies

article_metadata.title: Few health care options for low-income Kansans | The Wichita Eagle

og.description: A commentary by Rep. Dan Hawkins, R-Wichita, was disappointing to read, as it did not reflect the reality I see every day as a practicing physician and chief medical officer of GraceMed Health Clinic.
